pageContext.claim: “If I ever said something so mortifyingly stupid, the Fake News Media would come down on me with a vengeance. This is beyond a normal mistake [Biden saying 120 million people had died from covid-19, before immediately correcting himself and saying 120,000, which was edited out of this video Trump tweeted]. Why isn't the media reporting it?”
pageContext.analysis: Biden immediately corrected himself to say 120,000.
